Ice city Harbin has bitterly cold winter with average temperature of 20-30 degree below zero. All the houses in Harbin are equiped with heater system. Please just follow some tips to keep yourself from freezing outdoor.  

What to wear for Harbin winter sightseeing:  
Upper dressing is Cold-proof underclothes, woolen sweater and down coat or ski wear; 
Under dressing is woolen underpants and ski pants;  
Waterproof cotton high boots or comfortable shoes and socks for foot can be bought in Harbin less than $20;
